description:
The Warhammer 40,000 and Warhammer Age of Sigmar battleforces are up for pre-order next weekend! You'll also be able to go grilling behind enemy lines with a fantastic commemorative Astra Militarum miniature. Take a look at what's on the way: https://www.warhammer-community.com/en-gb/articles/0kkusrqx/sunday-preview-load-up-on-the-new-christmas-battleforces/
